rows.label: bf01120100_0010
rows.name:
They're bringing out the [System:Ruby rt=Powerfull tidal current ]Uzushio[/System:Ruby], huh.
The chairman's really going all out.

rows.label: bf01120100_0020
rows.name:
What are you getting so excited 
about over a ship like this?

rows.label: bf01120100_0030
rows.name: You really are such a child.

rows.label: bf01120100_0040
rows.name:
Being a child or adult 
has nothing to do with it.

rows.label: bf01120100_0050
rows.name: Can't you tell how amazing this ship is?

rows.label: bf01120100_0060
rows.name: I'm saying naive people are such a pain.

rows.label: bf01120100_0070
rows.name:
Acting all high and mighty
 when we're about the same age...

rows.label: bf01120100_0080
rows.name:
Ah, that rope there.
If you step on it when we depart, you'll get caught.

rows.label: bf01120100_0090
rows.name: and your leg will be torn off.

rows.label: bf01120100_0130
rows.name: Looks like we're both naive, aren't we?

rows.label: bf01120100_0150
rows.name:
Rex, we're heading out.
There's no one seeing you off, right?

rows.label: bf01120100_0160
rows.name:
You got night watch.
Till then, rest up inside.
